<?php

// Messages from expeditions.

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_1"] = 'Besides some quaint, small pets from a unknown marsh planet, this expedition brings nothing thrilling back from the trip.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_2"] = 'Despite the first, very promising scans of this sector, we unfortunately returned empty handed.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_3"] = 'A failure in the flagships reactor core nearly destroys the entire expedition fleet. Fortunately the technicians were more than competent and could avoid the worst. The repairs took quite some time and forced the expedition to return without having accomplished its goal.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_4"] = 'A living being made out of pure energy came aboard and induced all the expedition members into some strange trance, causing them to only gazed at the hypnotizing patterns on the computer screens. When most of them finally snapped out of the hypnotic-like state, the expedition mission needed to be aborted as they had way to little Deuterium.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_5"] = 'Your expedition has learnt about the extensive emptiness of space. There was not even one small asteroid or radiation or particle that could have made this expedition interesting. Your expedition has learnt about the extensive emptiness of space. There was not even one small asteroid or radiation or particle that could have made this expedition interesting.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_6"] = 'Your expedition took gorgeous pictures of a super nova. Nothing new could be obtained from the expedition, but at least there is good chance to win that "Best Picture Of The Universe" competition in next months issue of OGame magazine.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_7"] = 'Well, now we know that those red, class 5 anomalies do not only have chaotic effects on the ships navigation systems but also generate massive hallucination on the crew. The expedition didn\'t bring anything back.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_8"] = 'A strange computer virus attacked the navigation system shortly after parting our home system. This caused the expedition fleet to fly in circles. Needless to say that the expedition wasn\'t really successful.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_9"] = 'Our expedition team came across a strange colony that had been abandoned eons ago. After landing, our crew started to suffer from a high fever caused by an alien virus. It has been learned that this virus wiped out the entire civilization on the planet. Our expedition team is heading home to treat the sickened crew members. Unfortunately we had to abort the mission and we come home empty handed.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_10"] = 'Due to a failure in the central computers of the flagship, the expedition mission had to be aborted. Unfortunately as a result of the computer malfunction, the fleet returns home empty handed.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_11"] = 'Your expedition fleet followed odd signals for some time. At the end they noticed that those signals where being sent from an old probe which was sent out generations ago to greet foreign species. The probe was saved and some museums of your home planet already voiced their interest.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOTHING_12"] = 'Your expedition nearly ran into a neutron stars gravitation field and needed some time to free itself. Because of that a lot of Deuterium was consumed and the expedition fleet had to come back without any results.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOT_DEPLETED_1"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: It seems that this part of the universe has not been explored yet.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_NOT_DEPLETED_2"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: It feels great to be the first ones traveling through an unexplored sector.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MIN_1"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: It seems that no human has been in this part of the galaxy before.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MIN_2"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: We found debris of ancient space ships. We are not the first ones here.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MIN_3"] = 'Logbook addition of the communication officer: We nearly had a collision with another expedition fleet. I did not believe that there would be others around here.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MED_1"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: We found proof indicating the presence of multiple expedition fleets in the area. We are returning home.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MED_2"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: We established friendly radio contact with some other expeditions in this sector.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MED_3"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: We celebrated the expeditions fulfillment with the crew members of another expedition fleet which where on their way in the same sector. They have nothing new to report.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MAX_1"] = 'Entry from the communications officers logbook: If we felt in danger we could return with all the other expeditions flying around here.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MAX_2"] = 'Entry from the communication officers logbook: If it goes on like this we\'ll have to place navigation buoys to handle all this traffic.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DEPLETED_MAX_3"] = 'Logbook entry of the communication officer: Maybe it would be more useful to open a souvenir store here than sending yet another expedition.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_WEAK_1"] = 'Your expedition fleet had an unfriendly first contact with an unknown species.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_WEAK_2"] = 'Some exotic looking ships attacked the expedition fleet without warning!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_WEAK_3"] = 'Our expedition was attacked by a small group of unknown ships!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_WEAK_4"] = 'The expeditions fleet reports contact with unknown ships. The sensor readings are not decipherable, but it seems that the alien ships are activating their weapon system.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_MED_1"] = 'An unknown species is attacking our expedition!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_MED_2"] = 'Your expedition fleet seems to have flown into territory that belongs to an unknown but really aggressive and warlike alien race.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_MED_3"] = 'The connection to our expedition fleet was interrupted for a short time. We could decrypt their last message. They are under heavy attack, the aggressors could not be identified.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_STRONG_1"] = 'Your expedition ran into an alien invasion fleet and reports heavy fighting!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ALIENS_STRONG_2"] = 'A large Armada of crystalline ships of unknown origin take a direct collision course with our expedition-fleet. We should assume the worst.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_WEAK_1"] = 'Some really desperate space pirates tried to capture our expedition fleet.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_WEAK_2"] = 'We needed to fight some pirates which were, fortunately, only a few.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_WEAK_3"] = 'We caught some radio transmissions from some drunk pirates. Seems like we will be under attack soon.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_WEAK_4"] = 'Our expedition reports that a Moa Tikarr and his wild troops request our unconditional capitulation. If they are going to get serious they will have to learn that our ships are able to defend themselves.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_WEAK_5"] = 'Some primitive barbarians are attacking us with spaceships that can\'t even be named as such. If the fire gets serious we will be forced to fire back.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_MED_1"] = 'Your expedition had an unpleasant rendezvous with some space pirates.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_MED_2"] = 'We ran straight into an ambush set by some Star Buccaneers! A fight couldn\'t be avoided.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_MED_3"] = 'That emergency signal that the expedition team followed was in reality an ambush set up by some Star Buccaneers. A fight could not be avoided.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_STRONG_1"] = 'The recorded signals didn\'t come from a foreign being but from a secret pirate base! They were not really surprised by our presence in their sector.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_PIRATES_STRONG_2"] = 'The expedition reports tough battles against unidentified pirate ships!';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_SMALL_1"] = 'The expedition was able to capture and store some Dark Matter.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_SMALL_2"] = 'We found the remains of an alien ship. We found a little container with some Dark Matter on a shelf in the cargo hold!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_SMALL_3"] = 'Our expedition took over a ghost ship which was transporting a small amount of Dark Matter. We didn\'t find any hints of what happened to the original crew of the ship, but our technicians where able to rescue the Dark Matter.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_SMALL_4"] = 'We met an odd alien on the shelf of a small ship who gave us a case with Dark Matter in exchange for some simple mathematical calculations.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_SMALL_5"] = 'The expedition followed some odd signals to an asteroid. In the asteroids core a small amount of Dark Matter was found. The asteroid was taken and the explorers are attempting to extract the Dark Matter.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_MED_1"] = 'Our expedition accomplished a unique experiment. They were able to harvest Dark Matter from a dying star.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_MED_2"] = 'Our Expedition located a rusty space station, which seemed to have been floating uncontrolled through outer space for a long time. The station itself was totally useless, however, it was discovered that some Dark Matter is stored in the reactor. Our technicians are trying to save as much as they can.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_MED_3"] = 'Our expedition reports a spectacular phenomenon. The accumulation of Dark Matter in the energy storages of the ship shields. Our technicians try to store as much Dark Matter as they can while the phenomenon lasts.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_LARGE_1"] = 'A spontaneous hyper space deformation allowed your expedition to harvest large amount of Dark Matter!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DMFOUND_LARGE_2"] = 'Our expedition made first contact with a special race. It looks as though a creature made of pure energy, who named himself Legorian, flew through the expedition ships and then decided to help our underdeveloped species. A case containing Dark Matter materialized at the bridge of the ship!';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_LOST_1"] = 'The only thing left from the expedition was the following radio transmission: Zzzrrt Oh no! Krrrzzzzt That zrrrtrzt looks krgzzzz like .. AHH! Krzzzzzzzztzzzz...<br><br>\n\nTransmission terminated';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_LOST_2"] = 'A core meltdown of the lead ship leads to a chain reaction, which destroys the entire expedition fleet in a spectacular explosion.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_LOST_3"] = 'The last transmission we received from the expedition fleet was this magnificent picture of the opening of a black hole.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_LOST_4"] = 'Contact with the expedition fleet was suddenly lost. Our scientists are still trying to establish contact, but it seems the fleet is lost forever.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DELAY_1"] = 'Your navigator made a grave error in his computations that caused the expeditions jump to be miscalculated. Not only did the fleet miss the target completely, but the return trip will take a lot more time than originally planned.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DELAY_2"] = 'The solar wind of a red giant ruined the expeditions jump and it will take quite some time to calculate the return jump. There was nothing besides the emptiness of space between the stars in that sector. The fleet will return later than expected.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DELAY_3"] = 'The new navigation module is still buggy. The expeditions jump not only lead them in the wrong direction, but it used all the Deuterium fuel. Fortunately the fleets jump got them close to the departure planets moon. A bit disappointed the expedition now returns without impulse power. The return trip will take longer than expected.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DELAY_4"] = 'For unknown reasons the expeditions jump went totally wrong. It nearly landed in the heart of a sun. Fortunately it landed in a known system, but the jump back is going to take longer than thought.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DELAY_5"] = 'Your expedition went into a sector full of particle storms. This set the energy stores to overload and most of the ships main systems crashed. Your mechanics where able to avoid the worst, but the expedition is going to return with a big delay.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_DELAY_6"] = 'The expeditions flagship collided with a foreign ship when it jumped into the fleet without any warning. The foreign ship exploded and the damage to the flagship was substantial. As soon as the needed repair are carried out the fleet will begin to make their way back as the expedition can not continue in those conditions.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ACCEL_1"] = 'An unexpected back coupling in the energy spools of the engines hastened the expeditions return, it returns home earlier than expected. First reports tell they do not have anything thrilling to account for.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ACCEL_2"] = 'The new and daring commander successfully traveled through an unstable wormhole to shorten the flight back! However, the expedition itself didn\'t bring anything new.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_ACCEL_3"] = 'Your expeditions doesn\'t report any anomalies in the explored sector. But the fleet ran into some solar wind while returning. This resulted in the return trip being expedited. Your expedition returns home a bit earlier.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_SMALL_1"] = 'Your expedition discovered a small asteroid from which some resources could be harvested.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_SMALL_2"] = 'On an isolated planetoid we found some easily accessible resources fields and harvested some successfully.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_SMALL_3"] = 'The expedition found a radioactive planetoid with an extremely toxic atmosphere. After multiple scans, it shows that it has loads of resources. With the help of automated drones, we tried to harvest as many resources as possible.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_SMALL_4"] = 'Your expedition ran into some spaceship wrecks from an old battle. Some of the components could be saved and recycled.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_MED_1"] = 'Your expedition found an ancient, fully loaded but deserted freighter convoy. Some of the resources could be rescued.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_MED_2"] = 'On a tiny moon with its own atmosphere your expedition found some huge raw resources storage. The crew on the ground is trying to lift and load that natural treasure.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_MED_3"] = 'We met a small convoy of civil ships which needed food and medicine desperately. In exchange to that we got loads of useful resources.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_LARGE_1"] = 'Mineral belts around an unknown planet contained countless resources. The expedition ships are coming back and their storages are full!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_LARGE_2"] = 'Your expedition fleet reports the discovery of a giant alien ship wreck. They were not able to learn from their technologies but they were able to divide the ship into its main components and made some useful resources out of it.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_LOGBOOK_1"] = 'Entry from the first officers log book: We used all free space but we were still not able to take all resources found with us.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_LOGBOOK_2"] = 'Entry from the first officers log book: If only we had a few cargo ships more! Now we\'ll have to leave loads of resources behind.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_LOGBOOK_3"] = 'Entry from the first officers log book: We already threw away everything that we do not really need anymore but we are still not able to make enough space for all the resources found.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_RESFOUND_LOGBOOK_4"] = 'Entry from the first officers logbook: Even when we transformed the cafeteria and all the lounges into storages we still can\'t transport all the resources we found.';

$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_SMALL_1"] = 'We came across the remains of a previous expedition! Our technicians will try to get some of the ships to work again.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_SMALL_2"] = 'Your expedition ran into the shipyards of a colony that was deserted eons ago. In the shipyards hangar they discover some ships that could be salvaged. The technicians are trying to get some of them to fly again.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_SMALL_3"] = 'Our expedition found a planet which was almost destroyed during a certain chain of wars. There are different ships floating around in the orbit. The technicians are trying to repair some of them. Maybe we will also get information about what happened here.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_SMALL_4"] = 'We found a deserted pirate station. There are some old ships lying in the hangar. Our technicians are figuring out whether some of them are still useful or not.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_MED_1"] = 'We found the remains of an armada. The technicians directly went to the almost intact ships to try to get them to work again.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_MED_2"] = 'Our expedition ran into an old automatic shipyard. Some of the ships are still in the production phase and our technicians are currently trying to reactivate the yards energy generators.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_LARGE_1"] = 'We found an enormous spaceship graveyard. Some of the technicians from the expedition fleet were able to get some of the ships to work again.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_LARGE_2"] = 'We found the planet of an extinct civilization. We are able to see a giant intact space station, orbiting. Some of your technicians and pilots went to the surface looking for some ships which could still be used.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_LOGBOOK_1"] = 'Entry from the machines officers logbook: Had we brought some more ships with us, it would have been easy to take some of those beauties with us!';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_LOGBOOK_2"] = 'Entry from the machines officers logbook: Unfortunately, we did not have the capacity to bring back all the ships discovered in our mission.';
$LOCA["en"]["EXP_FLEET_LOGBOOK_3"] = 'Entry from the machines officers logbook: We unfortunately do not have enough capacity to bring all the found ships back.';
